This is a placeholder for the beep.mp3 sound file.

To complete the implementation of the game:
1. Replace this placeholder with an actual beep.mp3 sound file (short, less than 0.5 seconds)
2. You can find free sound files from sources like Freesound.org
3. Make sure the file is named exactly "beep.mp3" and is in this directory
4. The file should be small (under 100KB) for optimal performance

Without this sound file, the game's timer functionality will not work properly.